      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation. While it runs well, the exterior shows its age with various scratches, a few minor dings, and some paint fading on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has visible wear and a few small stains, though all essential electronics and the air conditioning are fully functional. It is a solid, honest car that has been maintained mechanically but definitely shows the signs of its years on the road.",
